<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Offer Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .offer-box {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #16a34a;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .validity-note {
            background-color: #fef9c3;
            border-left: 4px solid #eab308;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #713f12;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Pharma ERP — HR</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title">Congratulations, {{candidateName}}!</h1>

            <p>We are pleased to extend an offer of employment. Please review the details below:</p>

            <div class="offer-box">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Position</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{jobTitle}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Department</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{department}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Annual Salary</span>
                    <span class="info-value highlight">₹{{salary}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Start Date</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{startDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Reporting To</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{reportingManager}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="validity-note">
                This offer is valid until <strong>{{offerValidTill}}</strong>. Please accept before this date.
            </div>

            <p>To accept this offer, click the button below:</p>

            <a href="{{acceptanceUrl}}" class="cta-button">Accept Offer</a>

            <p>If you have any questions regarding this offer, please reach out to our HR team.</p>

            <p>We look forward to welcoming you to the team!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Pharma ERP HR system.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
